snippet.title: over the hill - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore the world in the golden age of offroading. Drive iconic vehicles from the 60s to 80s by yourself or with friends through challenging trails and beautiful scenery.

Wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2929250/over_the_hill/

Explore, navigate, and uncover the vast wilderness in over the hill, the newest installation from the creator of art of rally. Ramble your way through varied biomes inspired by real-world locations, from valleys to mountains and everything in between. Take a friend or go on a solo tour. Challenge yourself, collaborate with up to three friends, or just enjoy the sights - the world is your oyster.

Website: https://www.funselektor.com/overthehill
Discord: https://discord.gg/kcVbHR9
Twitter: https://twitter.com/funselektor
Instagram: https://instagram.com/funselektor
Strelka Games: https://twitter.com/StrelkaGames

Trailer: Bapho https://www.linkedin.com/in/enrico-capraro-91344a155/
Music: Tatreal https://tatreal.bandcamp.com/
